     fhir:Narrative.div "<div xml:lang=\"en\" lang=\"en\"><hr/><p><b>English</b></p><hr/><p class=\"res-header-id\"><b>Generated Narrative: ConceptMap mappingParticipantCDAFHIR</b></p><a name=\"en-mappingParticipantCDAFHIR\"> </a><a name=\"en-hcmappingParticipantCDAFHIR\"> </a><p>This mapping does not specify any particular context of use.</p><br/><p><b>Group 1 </b>Mapping from <code>https://interop.esante.gouv.fr/ig/document/core/StructureDefinition/fr-lm-participant</code> to <code>https://interop.esante.gouv.fr/ig/document/core/StructureDefinition/fr-cda-participant</code></p><table class=\"grid\"><tr><td><b>Source Code</b></td><td><b>Relationship</b></td><td><b>Target Code</b></td><td><b>Comment</b></td></tr><tr><td>FRLMParticipant</td><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R5/codesystem-concept-map-relationship.html#equivalent\" title=\"equivalent\">is equivalent to</a></td><td>participant</td><td/></tr><tr><td>FRLMParticipant.typeParticipation</td><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R5/codesystem-concept-map-relationship.html#equivalent\" title=\"equivalent\">is equivalent to</a></td><td>participant@typeCode</td><td/></tr><tr><td>FRLMParticipant.roleFonctionnel</td><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R5/codesystem-concept-map-relationship.html#equivalent\" title=\"equivalent\">is equivalent to</a></td><td>participant.functionCode</td><td/></tr><tr><td>FRLMParticipant.dateDebutEtOuFinParticipation</td><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R5/codesystem-concept-map-relationship.html#equivalent\" title=\"equivalent\">is equivalent to</a></td><td>participant.time</td><td/></tr><tr><td>FRLMParticipant.participant</td><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R5/codesystem-concept-map-relationship.html#equivalent\" title=\"equivalent\">is equivalent to</a></td><td>participant.associatedEntity</td><td>L'élément participant est de type PersonneStructure</td></tr></table><hr/><p><b>Group 2 </b>Mapping from <code>https://interop.esante.gouv.fr/ig/document/core/StructureDefinition/fr-cda-participant</code> to <a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/uv/fhir-clinical-document/STU1.1/StructureDefinition-ParticipantExtension.html\">Participant Extensionversion: 1.1.0)</a></p><table class=\"grid\"><tr><td><b>Source Code</b></td><td><b>Relationship</b></td><td><b>Target Code</b></td><td><b>Comment</b></td></tr><tr><td>participant</td><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R5/codesystem-concept-map-relationship.html#equivalent\" title=\"equivalent\">is equivalent to</a></td><td>extension:ParticipantExtension</td><td/></tr><tr><td>participant@typeCode</td><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R5/codesystem-concept-map-relationship.html#equivalent\" title=\"equivalent\">is equivalent to</a></td><td>extension:ParticipantExtension.extention:type</td><td/></tr><tr><td>participant.functionCode</td><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R5/codesystem-concept-map-relationship.html#equivalent\" title=\"equivalent\">is equivalent to</a></td><td>extension:ParticipantExtension.extention:function.coding</td><td/></tr><tr><td>participant.time</td><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R5/codesystem-concept-map-relationship.html#equivalent\" title=\"equivalent\">is equivalent to</a></td><td>extension:ParticipantExtension.extention:time</td><td/></tr><tr><td>participant.associatedEntity</td><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R5/codesystem-concept-map-relationship.html#equivalent\" title=\"equivalent\">is equivalent to</a></td><td>extension:ParticipantExtension.party</td><td>extension:party.ValueReference.resolve().ofType(PractitionerRole)</td></tr><tr><td>participant.associatedEntity@classCode</td><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R5/codesystem-concept-map-relationship.html#equivalent\" title=\"equivalent\">is equivalent to</a></td><td>extension:ParticipantExtension.party.PractitionerRole.qualification.code</td><td/></tr><tr><td>participant.associatedEntity.id</td><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R5/codesystem-concept-map-relationship.html#equivalent\" title=\"equivalent\">is equivalent to</a></td><td>e